<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> Madison, James. (8 February 1788) <a href="http://www.foundingfathers.info/federalistpapers/fed51.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.foundingfathers.info/federalistpapers/fed51.htm" rel="nofollow">"The Structure of the Government Must Furnish the Proper Checks and Balances Between the Different Departments"</a> <i>The Federalist Papers No. 51</i></li>
